---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer id="contact" class="section pt-0">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="card p-10 md:p-14 text-center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Contact / お問い合わせ</span>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-display-lg font-semibold">
        神山で、あなたの未来をはじめよう。
      </h2>
      <p class="en mt-3">Start your future in Kamiyama.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <a href="https://kamiyama.ac.jp/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="btn-primary no-underline">
          公式サイトへ
          <span class="text-paper/70 text-xs ml-1">Official site</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-ink-muted">
      <p>
        © {year} 神山まるごと高専 紹介LP（非公式デモ） / Unofficial demo site
      </p>
      <p class="en">
        Built with Astro &amp; Tailwind — deployed on GitHub Pages.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
